# VulnSploit Mobile

Read `IMPLEMENTATION.md` and `docs/MOBILE_APP_BRIEF.md` before implementing.

## Stack
Expo SDK 52 · TypeScript · Expo Router · TanStack Query · Zustand · Axios · expo-secure-store

## API
Base: `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` + `/api`. Auth: JWT Bearer + refresh on 401.
Use `POST /api/recon/` for full recon (NOT `/api/sessions/`).

## Phases
0 scaffold ✅ → 1 auth → 2 dashboard → 3 scans → 4 recon → 5 reports → 6 offline → 7 polish

## Design
Cyber theme: bg `#000000`, primary `#3b82f6`, mono font. Brand VULN+SPLOIT. Legal disclaimer on scan screens.

## Paths
- Screens: `app/`
- Logic: `src/`
